        {"4c9540b69476fc83972e47bc339833f61e6f8e09c20442f05089484f6c1dbe7f":1,"eb02eb654c6f8be899e9aab33ce57d421964178b3bc15f9bb89b2da672a98a7d":73,"6a453c4287c6a10f06fa2a63d6bcab5f4622cd063892dd96a9495dcad653ee10":3,"ee8e47e42b73e98f4de06ec8a0fe98bda62b02b3177e7bc03bc3784a5fa581d7":"由神秘人物「拉比林斯達」所組成，探究世界之謎的公會。僅由少數幾位信賴的過的人所組成。表面是在經營著可麗餅店，但其實是假扮成普通公會的祕密結社。","3e48d6b6c02852df74a7eaf1547e4f31d732ea34c7f3bc6601e956063c241951":"拉比林斯","6507aa7262ee52bccfd2b5a43d5b2568ed8a5ec498ea8afcfa996be618148a8f":3010,"fa00064a23be9e761e5a2c72332dcebfe06bda97061b6d2e6a034e62c6418082":0},
